data.description:
Welcome to a haven of modern elegance and entertaining excellence! Nestled in the Victory community, this stunning, two-year-new home is a paradise for those who love to host & create lasting memories. As you step into the expansive family room, a world of possibilities unfolds, seamlessly connected to a gourmet kitchen that beckons culinary adventures. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring exquisite dove-tailed, soft-close cabinetry and granite countertops. The large island takes center stage, creating a perfect hub for entertaining guests & hosting lively gatherings. High-end appliances, including double ovens & a gas stove top, elevate your culinary experiences to new heights. Adjacent to the kitchen is a spacious dining area, ideal for those special eat-in occasions. Imagine the joy of sharing meals with loved ones in this inviting space. Step through the sliding door onto the patio, where a breathtaking panorama unfolds  a large turfed backyard, a 14 Ft swim spa, and a stunning mountain view set the stage for outdoor entertainment like no other.
The allure extends beyond the kitchen and outdoor space. Picture yourself unwinding by the custom fire pit with a glass of wine, basking in the afterglow of a day spent on the pickleball courts, a perfect blend of relaxation and recreation.
This thoughtfully designed home offers a 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom layout with a split floor plan, ensuring privacy and convenience for both residents and guests. The beautiful owner's suite is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring a spacious bathroom and a walk-in closet  the perfect retreat after a day of festivities.
Practicality meets style in the large 3-car garage, equipped with custom storage cabinets to keep your space organized and clutter-free. The upgraded laundry room and lovely tile throughout the home contribute to the overall ease of maintenance, allowing you to focus on enjoying your beautiful surroundings.
As the ultimate bonus, a 2.62% assumable V.A. Loan adds a valuable financial advantage, making this home even more enticing. Don't miss the chance to explore this exceptional property; come see it today and start envisioning the countless events and gatherings you'll soon be able to host in your dream home!
